      "title": "Chili Powder",
      "description": "A quick spice blend for adding heat and depth to chili, sauces, and marinades.",
      "instructions": "Whisk the paprika, oregano, cumin, garlic powder, onion powder, and cayenne pepper together in a small bowl until evenly combined.\nTransfer to an airtight container.\nStore in a cool, dry place.",
